/author-eBGdtm3O4c2NQ7sIhikeXg">Dương Thận</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Th%E1%BA%ADp-nguy%E1%BB%87t-th%E1%BA%ADp-c%E1%BB%ADu-nh%E1%BA%ADt-v%C3%A3ng-b%C3%A1i-V%E1%BB%A5-B%E1%BA%A3n-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-ti%C3%AAn-sinh-k%E1%BB%B5-nh%E1%BA%ADt/poem-M6BK1F7J45h0CFyRDx1-jg">Thập nguyệt thập cửu nhật vãng bái Vụ Bản Trần tiên sinh kỵ nhật - 十月十九日往拜務本陳先生忌日</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Th%C3%B9-m%C3%A2u-1/poem-xk7xxanHaMU6GdkrLCNcwQ">Thù mâu 1 - 綢繆 1</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/V%E1%BA%A5n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-s%C6%B0-t%E1%BA%ADt/poem-v65jq0YrqWTa0P31WflpAA">Vấn Phúc Đường đại sư tật - 問福堂大師疾</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/author-vnduJD_TYrIrUDl9fyOqRw">Tuệ Trung thượng sĩ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
